text: József Gyönyörű (19 March 1925 - 18 September 1999) was a Hungarian sports shooter. He competed in the 25 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:1999 deaths Category:Hungarian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Hungary Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Hajdú-Bihar County
